Love you posters. I do. But we've started something here that's going to screw up the numbering for the whole season. 

The first TWO episodes of season 6 were released on the same night, Broken Pt. 1 & 2 premiered Sept. 21st. That makes what I assume this posted episode is, "The Tyrant," episode 4. 

If this is actually "Epic Fail," aka, S06e03, then my apologies.

No, this is actually "The Tyran", aka S06E03.
